                    ],
                    Texts: [
                        {
                            Text: "You are standing in an active yield zone. Highfield Estate is the highest parcel we hold, terraced up the mountain shelf on the Scorchspire road. The family that cut these steps into the ridge has been transitioned to alternative outcomes, and the estate now performs. Rows. Numbers. Thin air and performance."
                        },
                        {
                            Text: "I run a string of fields off one clipboard. Highfield is the crown of it - the parcel closest to the mountain, closest to the Frontier road, the one the Board asks about by name."
                        }
                    ],
                    Name: "Manager - the quota",
                    Label: "quota"
